efore the Masters, where he tied for third.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stake.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Morikawa\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the Memorial\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"the Masters\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A tie for ninth at the RBC Heritage, a tie for fourth at the PGA Championship and a fourth at the Charles Schwab Challenge helped his cause.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RBC_Heritage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RBC Heritage\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q15061650\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RBC_Heritage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RBC_Heritage\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Schwab_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999998863132, \"rank\": 1.1394566039278341e-10, \"text\": \"Charles Schwab\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Schwab_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_Schwab_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A tie\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"a tie\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"the PGA Championship\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"his cause\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cantlay has not helped himself of late, with a tie for 53rd at the PGA and a missed cut at the Memorial.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cantlay\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"a tie\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"53rd\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"the PGA\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"a missed cut\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"the Memorial\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic format takes two players per country based on the Official World Golf Ranking.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic format\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"two players\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"the Official World Golf Ranking\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top 15 are eligible with a maximum of two per country beyond the top 15.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a maximum\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theofficial Olympic ranking is here, updated each Monday after tournaments.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theofficial Olympic ranking\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it is setting up to be a good tournament.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good tournament\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rory McIlroy and Shane Lowry should play for Ireland; Viktor Hovland for Norway; Tommy Fleetwood and Matt Fitzpatrick for Great Britain; Ludvig Aberg for Sweden; Tom Kim and Ben An for South Korea; Hideki Matsuyama for Japan; Jon Rahm and David Puig for Spain; Nick Taylor and Corey Conners for Canada; Jason Day and Min Woo Lee for Australia; Joaquin Niemann for Chile; Matteo Manassero for Italy.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2346, \"end\": 2358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory McIlroy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q1315670