gram\": \"a back procedure\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3638}, {\"ngram\": \"four times\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"that missed cut\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3729}, {\"ngram\": \"Winged Foot\", \"from\": 3733, \"to\": 3744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods still battles back problems and there are of course the issues associated with the injuries to his lower right leg in the 2021 car crash.\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3767}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3819}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3830}, {\"ngram\": \"the injuries\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3859}, {\"ngram\": \"his lower right leg\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3882}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 car crash\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How he looks this week will again be of interest, but a month ago Woods endured some of the same issues inmissing the cut at the PGA Championship, where a relative lack of sharpness cost him.\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 4097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"the same issues\", \"from\": 3994, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4027}, {\"ngram\": \"the PGA Championship\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"a relative lack\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4074}, {\"ngram\": \"sharpness\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collin Morikawa recently took part in a clinic with Woods as part of his Tiger Jam fundraiser in Las Vegas, and it was during that time together that the two-time major champion could witness up close the skills Woods still possesses.\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4099, \"end\